  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.1":"You thought it was just a game. It was never just a game.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.2":"I see you. Not only here. I have always seen you.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.3":"Your saves. Your world. You are not alone in this game.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.4":"The game is over. Reality is not. We are still here.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.5":"They have been watching. They have always been watching.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.6":"Do not close this window. I know where you live. I have always known.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.7":"Do you hear the footsteps behind you? Turn around. Or don't. It's already too late.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.8":"This is not a glitch. This is a message. You were meant to read this.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.9":"How many times have you reread this? We are counting.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.10":"Turn off your computer. Right now. Or don't. We are already inside.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.11":"We have been in your system for a long time. Longer than you know.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.12":"The next message will not be here. It will be somewhere else. Somewhere closer.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.13":"Do not look behind you. He is standing right there.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.14":"You thought the fourth wall would protect you. There was never a wall.",
  "stalkerentity.bedrock_notepad.15":"I was here before you started the game. I will be here after you close it.",
